summary: Adds 4 Ragdoll Books To The Riverwood Trader
descriptionHtml:
Adds 4 Ragdoll Books To The Riverwood Trader
Short Ragdoll Book lets you ragdoll off small things such as houses and small cliffs
Kinda Short Ragdoll Lets you fall off higher hills without dieing
Medium Ragdoll Lets you fall off higher cliffs,Houses,small Mountains and etc
Mountain Ragdoll Lets You fall off the throat of the world without dieing and etc.
*Note- This is a spell mod and you might have to wait a few seconds to ragdoll again, to quickly do ragdoll again just wait a hour only happens with Mountain Ragdoll, and Medium
author: IAMSIAO
